  rcases getFunctorPushforwardStructure H‚ÇÇ with ‚ü®X‚ÇÇ, f‚ÇÇ, h‚ÇÇ, hf‚ÇÇ, rfl‚ü©
  suffices ‚Ñ±.val.map (g‚ÇÅ ‚â´ h‚ÇÅ).op (x f‚ÇÅ hf‚ÇÅ) = ‚Ñ±.val.map (g‚ÇÇ ‚â´ h‚ÇÇ).op (x f‚ÇÇ hf‚ÇÇ) by
    simpa using this
